  "text": "We examined whether POVPC would induce pyroptosis (inflammasome-mediated cell death) by measuring lactate dehydrogenase release [CITATION_1] . POVPC induced lactate dehydrogenase release in a dose-and time-dependent manner in BMDMs (Supplemental Fig. 1A-D) , showing that pyroptosis is accompanied by POVPC-induced inflammasome activation.",
